    <h1>Property Registration and Stamp Duty in India 2026: State-by-State Guide</h1>
    <div class="article-dateline">
      <span class="article-dateline__item"><span class="article-dateline__label">Published:</span> 25 March 2026</span>
      <span class="article-dateline__sep">·</span>
