    <p class="blog-article__intro">When you budget for a home, you calculate the price, the EMI, the down payment. What most first-time buyers discover too late: stamp duty and registration charges add ₹4–7 lakh to an ₹80 lakh flat — money that must be paid in cash, not through your home loan. This guide covers current rates across major states and how to minimise them legally.</p>

